claim.claim-text:
1. A microelectronic die comprising: 
first and second differential signal lines on a first metal layer of the microelectronic die to carry a differential signal within the microelectronic die, said first and second differential signal lines being substantially parallel to one another; 
wherein each of said first and second differential signal lines provides a return path for a signal on the other of said first and second differential signal lines, said return path being the predominant return path for each respective signal.
